overview: In his latest stand-up comedy special, Savantsyndrom (Savant Syndrome), Swedish comedian Jonas Strandberg realizes that his life is not his own. Strolling the streets of Stockholm, he finally decides - he's just not sure what he decides, but it all ends up at a darkly-lit club in Stockholm where he performs his 20-minutes set with one-liners.
title: Savantsyndrom
